cold shoe
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number: 1
Definition:to provide a horse with a replacement shoe between blacksmith visits [using clippers and rasps to fashion shoe and fit it to hoof without using heat.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
